- Computer or two players?
- If computer, select easy AI or hard AI
- If two players then ask names
- Ask the size of the board
- Ask how many ships
- Select from ship types
- Randomly place ships or place them on your own
- Cli colors for ships
- Players play in turns
- If ship is hit that part turns red
- If all ships are sunk player loses.
- Congratulate the winner!
- Show scores
- Local storage for high scores
- Multiplayer over net

